Package: light
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Backlight control
 Light is a program to control backlight controllers under GNU/Linux,
 it is the successor of lightscript, which was a bash script with 
 the same purpose, and tries to maintain the same functionality.
